/mamamoo-hwasas-fierce-mama-look-has-gone-viral-korea|title=MAMAMOO Hwasa's fierce MAMA look has gone viral in Korea|website=SBS PopAsia}}</ref> [[Iggy Azalea]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.idolator.com/7530968/iggy-azalea-black-widow-video-beyonce-influence?chrome=1|title=Iggy Azalea's Sexy \"Black Widow\" Look Was (Partly) Inspired By Beyonce: Find Out How|date=August 14, 2014}}</ref> [[Jessica Sanchez]],<ref>{{cite news|last=Varga|first=George|url=http://www.utsandiego.com/news/2012/mar/20/chat-american-idols-jessica-sanchez/|title=A chat with local 'Idol' Jessica Sanchez|work=[[U-T San Diego]]|publisher=MLIM Holdings|date=March 20, 2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905225441/http://www.utsandiego.com/news/2012/mar/20/chat-american-idols-jessica-sanchez/|archivedate=September 5, 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref> [[Jessie J]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/news/jessie-j-beyonce-is-inspirational-28652275.html|title=Jessie J: Beyonce is inspirational|work=The Belfast Telegraph}}</ref> [[JoJo (singer)|JoJo]],<ref>{{cite web|last=Fine|first=Audrey|url=http://www.seventeen.com/entertainment/features/interview-jojo|title=Interview with JoJo|website=Seventeen.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100917084825/http://www.seventeen.com/entertainment/features/interview-jojo|archivedate=September 17, 2010|url-status=live}}</ref> [[Kelly Rowland]],<ref>{{cite web|last=Moss|first=Corey|title=Kelly Rowland Scraps Sappy Story, Picks Up Snoop|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1541798/20060926/rowland_kelly.jhtml|publisher=MTV News|date=September 27, 2006|accessdate=April 12, 2008}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://photos.essence.com/galleries/kelly_rowland__style_icons|title=Kelly Rowland: Style Icons|website=Essence|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110814181818/http://photos.essence.com/galleries/kelly_rowland__style_icons|archivedate=August 14, 2011|url-status=dead |access-date=October 20, 2012}}</ref> [[Kendrick Lamar]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eonline.com/uk/news/872486/kendrick-lamar-on-what-he-learned-from-beyonce-and-why-he-won-t-talk-about-donald-trump|title=Kendrick Lamar on What He Learned From Beyonc\u00e9 and Why He Won't Talk About Donald Trump|date=August 9, 2017|website=E! News}}</ref> [[Lady Gaga]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1664720/lady-gaga-beyonce-inside-the-outside/|title=Lady Gaga Recalls Beyonc\u00e9's Inspiration in MTV's 'Inside The Outside'|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=September 27, 2014}}</ref> [[Little Mix]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://fuse.tv/videos/2017/02/rep-your-ladies-little-mix-interview-beyonce|title=Little Mix Discuss Authenticity & Why Beyonc\u00e9 Inspires Them|first=Rep Your|last=Ladies|website=Fuse}}</ref> [[Meghan Trainor]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://radio.com/2014/07/31/meghan-trainor-interview-all-about-that-bass-new-music-to-know/|title=New Music To Know: Meghan Trainor Doesn't Care if You're Ready For This Jelly|website=Radio.com|accessdate=January 11, 2016 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819075822/http://radio.com/2014/07/31/meghan-trainor-interview-all-about-that-bass-new-music-to-know/ | archive-date=August 19, 2014 | url-status=dead}}</ref> [[Nicole Scherzinger]],<ref>{{cite news|last=Moran|first=Jonathan|url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/entertainment/insider/former-pussycat-doll-frontwoman-nicole-scherzinger-talks-about-her-racy-new-single-and-her-love-for-boyfriend-lewis-hamilton/story-e6frewt9-1226127165343|title=Former Pussycat Dolls frontwoman Nicole Scherzinger talks about her racy new single and her love for boyfriend Lewis Hamilton|work=[[The Daily Telegraph (Sydney)|The Daily Telegraph]]|date=September 4, 2011|accessdate=September 6, 2011}}</ref> [[Millie Bobby Brown]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GW80IH-qpH4|title=Millie Bobby Brown Shares a Brilliant Amy Winehouse Impersonation|via=YouTube}}</ref> [[Rihanna]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ctestp.ctv.ca/